{"title":"收获时节","authors":["丁可"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":10,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁可"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那把镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经那位大胡子淬火之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成一柄弯月形的青锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗照中国的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖南韶山一个农家子弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握起镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手指试了试钢口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后俯下身去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把镰伸向黑夜的根部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找到了一种最适合中国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收割姿式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此中国的田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔着镰刀的精魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他率领"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群农家孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥起镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一镰一镰　收割到天安门前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然是一柄青锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么　人民的信任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是金黄的鞘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年的青铜与铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写成了收割史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有那把血火中抽出的镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最胜任收获中国的命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年过去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我童年的记忆里　仍弥漫着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那把贴依着红色棉布的镰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘下的青草与稻菽的鲜味"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"３"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子收割的前夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见须发如霜的父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下磨着镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯月形镰刀与磨石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出砥砺时的嚓嚓声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一滴滴水撩在磨石上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许还有父亲的眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月是镰刀群游的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的父亲凫游在麦水中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为找到了一把好镰而欣喜若狂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弦月一样升起来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那把经过擦拭磨砺的镰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到稻谷中间　回到麦子中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们的土地以柔和的折射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们的父亲以称心的手感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远像初初入学的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见削铅笔的小刀那样亲切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：江苏沛县文化馆）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}